{"tid":142103,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[科學題]你哋仲記唔記得人體係由咩物質組成？","createTime":"2017-03-03T12:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T13:25:13.000Z","uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40074e5eb1c26d13c3f84a9e55406620486d851a","tid":142103,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:52:43.000Z","msg":"答案：水35公升，碳20公斤，氨水4公升，石灰1.5公斤，磷800克，鹽250克，硝石100克，琉黃80克，氟7.5克，鐵5克，硅3克，另外仲有15種微量元素<br />\n<br />\n呢啲物質連細路仔都夠錢買，人類嘅身體其實只係好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係就冇人可以成功咁鍊成到一個完整嘅身體，其中究竟欠缺咗乜嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43241b5aee7e31b16a76b4f554b4a8fbdf875eb2","tid":142103,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"掙扎"},{"pid":"a7773fb08eb966e152ae5b5e76cdef9bb9cd0bd3","tid":142103,"uid":1423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:54:11.000Z","msg":"真理"},{"pid":"db5057b418c565064604da8fe50861d11a651fad","tid":142103,"uid":9930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:55:17.000Z","msg":"係愛啊哈利"},{"pid":"88d5e82c686a1b19e378b73dc6eeeaaae3123f06","tid":142103,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真理</blockquote><br />\n唔係靈魂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c55635cea6a46608e9ffe9a60c429e9134595f","tid":142103,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真理</blockquote><br />\n唔係靈魂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩樣都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8f15daa084d4432dca7f029c6312912d7db3f3","tid":142103,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"鍊金術師"},{"pid":"81107