" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560c3bf6bf38ae11b0fda34d22fec5c9ef356460","tid":142103,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"精加卵"},{"pid":"06db5d3bd093a74bb65254ca696acefbc5948ea4","tid":142103,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>掙扎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比啲掙扎佢</blockquote><br />\n胡C Fum<span style=\"color: red;\">e</span>t<span style=\"color: red;\">a</span>l Alchemist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"458f51ef34ca13be122b7ad68a67817bfb6b42b2","tid":142103,"uid":39700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:06:10.000Z","msg":"食物（包括牛，豬，雞，人），氧--&gt;能量，水，二氧化碳 <br />\n<br />\n用反定律方程 <br />\n姐係我地仲差能量 <br />\n二氧化碳 係大氣之中都有<br />\n<br />\n根據E=mc^2<br />\n我地只需用樓主所講既物質 用光速轉兩次<br />\n就可以<br />\n點樣可以將物質變光 當係燒左佢 <br />\n記住要2次燒<br />\n<br />\n但燒都有次序<br />\n首先屋企關左窗<br />\n令人體可製造更多二氧化碳<br />\n幫助煉成<br />\n然後落碳先，燒左一陣再落水<br />\n再落其他野"},{"pid":"a34dd9689f27d40a9afd87d842c2ee44746cbae9","tid":142103,"uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"留名等睇人體鍊成"},{"pid":"6b422c3f0ae57f2bdcc1580dab5d3eb812942be9","tid":142103,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:07:50.000Z","msg":"鑽石都係炭黎架咋"},{"pid":"9072a073b0d5998c72db489beab24b54da07b